          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audio CD 9780743552684" href="/book/show/485019.The_Cold_Moon">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2428139742" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15320451924578004278">Some years ago I saw Denzil Washington as Lincoln Rhyme and Angelina Jolie as Amelia Sachs in the movie, THE BONE COLLECTOR. Since then when I read a Rhyme novel, I visualize these protagonists as portrayed in the movie. A good choice, I would say. This is another interesting case—actually two cases for Rhyme and his team to solve. If you can put aside some of the horrible things done to the victims, it is fascinating for me to learn how Rhyme unravels the mystery. There are twists and turns bef</span>
  <span id="freeText15320451924578004278" style="display:none">Some years ago I saw Denzil Washington as Lincoln Rhyme and Angelina Jolie as Amelia Sachs in the movie, THE BONE COLLECTOR. Since then when I read a Rhyme novel, I visualize these protagonists as portrayed in the movie. A good choice, I would say. This is another interesting case—actually two cases for Rhyme and his team to solve. If you can put aside some of the horrible things done to the victims, it is fascinating for me to learn how Rhyme unravels the mystery. There are twists and turns before the ending, and maybe even a twist in Rhyme’s and Sachs relationship. I have enjoyed reading a number of this series and look forward to more. </span>
  <a data-text-id="15320451924578004278" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

